subject: Automobile Racing
Nascar Nextel Cup Series
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Jimmie Johnson won a dramatic duel with Matt Kenseth at Texas Motor Speedway, grabbing his third consecutive victory and wresting the Nascar Nextel Cup points lead from Jeff Gordon.
